        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>path</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The path onto which to set the rotation </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>angle</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The absolute angle of the rotation. The angle is represented in the same way that is used with <ref refid="group___math_1gad373193b20c68af1004a9dc2c35c2e48" kindref="member">sin_lookup()</ref>. See <ref refid="group___math_1gade7adcdaf0a7aca734c444328afd6f77" kindref="member">TRIG_MAX_ANGLE</ref> for more information. </para>
