</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Setting a rotation does not affect the points in the path directly. The rotation is applied on-the-fly during drawing, either using <ref refid="group___path_drawing_1ga4aa5b80f8f98d2cb7e6701b39bb18e32" kindref="member">gpath_draw_filled()</ref> or <ref refid="group___path_drawing_1ga33e423daf4e125ae273111871159eead" kindref="member">gpath_draw_outline()</ref>. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
